name: eslint-config-airbnb
notes: ESLint shareable config from Airbnb for JavaScript and React linting. Extends eslint-config-airbnb-base and adds React-specific rules (eslint-plugin-react, eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y). ESLint configurations are JSON/JavaScript files that define linting rules, parser options, and plugin configurations for the ESLint linter. Used exclusively during development/CI workflows to enforce code style and catch errors. Not applicable to Workers which is a runtime environment, not a linting/development environment.
